(Bond state machine:) Tj
T*
(- pending -> active -> exiting -> unlockable -> withdrawn) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Stake state machine:) Tj
T*
(- pending -> active -> exiting -> unlockable -> withdrawn) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Both are enforced by deterministic height and confirmation checks. No state transition is) Tj
T*
(accepted if preconditions fail.) Tj
T*
(- Fee Routing and Pool Rules) Tj
T*
(- Fee uplift policy: +25%) Tj
T*
(- Fee pool routing:) Tj
T*
(- pre-tail \(height < 8,000,000\): 40% of total fees \(20% miner-side, 20% stake-side\),) Tj
T*
(- post-tail \(height >= 8,000,000\): 55% of total fees \(25% miner-side, 30% stake-side\).) Tj
T*
(- Miner-side split:) Tj
T*
(- pre-tail: 0% winner-proportional, 20% bonded-idle split \(of total fees\),) Tj
T*
(- post-tail: 20% winner-proportional, 5% bonded-idle split \(of total fees\).) Tj
T*
(- Burn policy at tail: 100% burn on routed non-pool fees \(45% of total fees at post-tail) Tj
T*
(routing, subject to floor clipping\).) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Consensus-managed pool address is deterministic and network-separated:) Tj
T*
(- mainnet: "P" + Base56\(SHA3-384\("ATHO_PROTOCOL_POOL_MAINNET"\)\)) Tj
T*
(- testnet: "L" + Base56\(SHA3-384\("ATHO_PROTOCOL_POOL_TESTNET"\)\)) Tj
T*
(- regnet: "L" + Base56\(SHA3-384\("ATHO_PROTOCOL_POOL_REGNET"\)\)) Tj
