(6.1 Slashable vs Non-Slashable) Tj
T*
(Slashable:) Tj
T*
(- PoW-valid block that is consensus-invalid \(miner proof, bond eligibility, tx validity,) Tj
T*
(structure, or reward correctness\).) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Not slashable:) Tj
T*
(- stale/orphan valid block from honest race,) Tj
T*
(- reorged-out valid block,) Tj
T*
(- late but otherwise valid relay.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(This distinction is deterministic and required for safe slashing enforcement.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
