T*
(block-mode conversion:) Tj
T*
(- private mempool form uses amount_plain,) Tj
T*
(- block form uses amount_commit,) Tj
T*
(- miner must recompute tx_id from canonical no-witness payload after conversion.) Tj
T*
() Tj
